  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Ball
    The Ball class creates a ball used in the game.

    The GameDriver class creates a window frame that allows the users to play the Ping Pong game
    GameFrame
    The GameFrame class creates the window for the game
    GamePanel
    The GamePanel class creates and adds all the attributes to the game, including the ball, paddles, and scoreboard.

    The Paddle class creates two paddles used in the game.
    Scoreboard
    The Scoreboard class keeps track of points made by both players
